<paragraph id="5E3D02A75654B2D64891605AF206DEB7" pageId="0" pageNumber="149">In honour of Professor Felix Sperling of the University of Alberta, Canada, who contributed profoundly to systematic research in entomology, and who maintains long-standing achievements as curator of the E. H. Strickland Entomological Museum (http://www.entomology.museums.ualberta.ca).</paragraph>
